msgstr "But then there was an intense burning in my body, "

msgctxt "mn85:25.5"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, rājakumāra, dve balavanto purisā dubbalataraṃ purisaṃ nānābāhāsu gahetvā aṅgārakāsuyā santāpeyyuṃ samparitāpeyyuṃ; "
msgstr "like two strong men grabbing a weaker man by the arms to burn and scorch him on a pit of glowing coals. "

msgctxt "mn85:25.6"
msgid "evameva kho me, rājakumāra, mukhato ca nāsato ca kaṇṇato ca assāsapassāsesu uparuddhesu adhimatto kāyasmiṃ ḍāho hoti. "
msgstr " "

