msgid "yassatthāya kulaputtā sammadeva agārasmā anagāriyaṃ pabbajanti, tadanuttaraṃ—brahmacariyapariyosānaṃ diṭṭheva dhamme sayaṃ abhiññā sacchikatvā upasampajja vihareyya satta vassāni. "
msgstr "realize the supreme end of the spiritual path in seven years. "

msgctxt "mn85:59.3"
msgid "Tiṭṭhantu, rājakumāra, satta vassāni. "
msgstr "Let alone seven years, "

msgctxt "mn85:59.4"
msgid "Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ labhamāno—"
msgstr "they could "

