msgctxt "mn85:59.37"
msgid "Tiṭṭhatu, rājakumāra, eko rattindivo. "
msgstr "Let alone one day, "

msgctxt "mn85:59.38"
msgid "Imehi pañcahi padhāniyaṅgehi samannāgato bhikkhu tathāgataṃ vināyakaṃ labhamāno sāyamanusiṭṭho pāto visesaṃ adhigamissati, pātamanusiṭṭho sāyaṃ visesaṃ adhigamissatī”ti. "
msgstr "when a mendicant with these five factors that support meditation has the Realized One as trainer, they could be instructed in the evening and achieve distinction in the morning, or be instructed in the morning and achieve distinction in the evening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya60
msgctxt "mn85:60.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, bodhi rājakumāro bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, Prince Bodhi said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "mn85:60.2"
msgid "“aho buddho, aho dhammo, aho dhammassa svākkhātatā. "
msgstr "“Oh, the Buddha! Oh, the teaching! Oh, how well explained is the teaching! "

msgctxt "mn85:60.3"
msgid "Yatra hi nāma sāyamanusiṭṭho pāto visesaṃ adhigamissati, pātamanusiṭṭho sāyaṃ visesaṃ adhigamissatī”ti. "
msgstr "For someone could be instructed in the evening and achieve distinction in the morning, or be instructed in the morning and achieve distinction in the evening.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: nya61, pts-vp-pli2.97, sc70
msgctxt "mn85:61.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, sañjikāputto māṇavo bodhiṃ rājakumāraṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he said this, Sañjikāputta said to Prince Bodhi, "

msgctxt "mn85:61.2"
msgid "“evameva panāyaṃ bhavaṃ bodhi: "
msgstr "“Though Master Bodhi speaks like this, "

#. VAR: vadeti → vadesi (si) | pavedeti (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "mn85:61.3"
msgid "‘aho buddho, aho dhammo, aho dhammassa svākkhātatā’ti ca vadeti; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "mn85:61.4"
msgid "atha ca pana na taṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañcā”ti. "
msgstr "you don’t go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn85:61.5"
msgid "“Mā hevaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, avaca; mā hevaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, avaca. "
msgstr "“Don’t say that, dear Sañjikāputta, don’t say that! "

# NOTE: Quotes in MS are incorrect.
msgctxt "mn85:61.6"
msgid "Sammukhā metaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, ayyāya sutaṃ, sammukhā paṭiggahitaṃ”. "
msgstr "I have heard and learned this in the presence of the lady, my mother. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.7"
msgid "“Ekamidaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, samayaṃ bhagavā kosambiyaṃ viharati ghositārāme. "
msgstr "This one time the Buddha was staying near Kosambi, in Ghosita’s Monastery. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.8"
msgid "Atha kho me ayyā kucchimatī yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. Ekamantaṃ nisinnā kho me ayyā bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then my pregnant mother went up to the Buddha, bowed, sat down to one side, and said to him, "

msgctxt "mn85:61.9"
msgid "‘yo me ayaṃ, bhante, kucchigato kumārako vā kumārikā vā so bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca. "
msgstr "‘Sir, the prince or princess in my womb goes for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.10"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ taṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan’ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may the Buddha remember them as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn85:61.11"
msgid "Ekamidaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, samayaṃ bhagavā idheva bhaggesu viharati susumāragire bhesakaḷāvane migadāye. "
msgstr "Another time the Buddha was staying here in the land of the Bhaggas on Crocodile Hill, in the deer park at Bhesakaḷā’s Wood. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.12"
msgid "Atha kho maṃ dhāti aṅkena haritvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi. Ekamantaṃ ṭhitā kho maṃ dhāti bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then my nurse, carrying me on her hip, went to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side, and said to him, "

msgctxt "mn85:61.13"
msgid "‘ayaṃ, bhante, bodhi rājakumāro bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca. "
msgstr "‘Sir, this Prince Bodhi goes for refuge to the Buddha, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.14"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ taṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan’ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may the Buddha remember him as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "mn85:61.15"
msgid "Esāhaṃ, samma sañjikāputta, tatiyakampi bhagavantaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṃghañca. "
msgstr "Now for a third time I go for refuge to the Buddha, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "mn85:61.16"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhagavā dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gatan”ti. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may the Buddha remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "mn85:61.17"
msgid "Bodhirājakumārasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

